New #WebGL pattern! 

A Voronoi diagram (love it) with eyes calculated over the polar coordinates of each cell. No images or graphic libs here, just a #GLSL shader wrapped with JS

Live demo & source code: https://t.co/oTIbjwqSUH

Hosted on @CodePen
